&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the teams&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Finance &amp;amp; Strategy: &lt;/strong&gt;Partners with senior leadership to inform strategy, long-range planning, and resource allocation. Work emphasizes strategic financial analysis, business modeling, and cross-functional partnership to influence product roadmap and go-to-market decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Treasury Finance: &lt;/strong&gt;Focuses on the company’s liquidity, cash management, capital allocation, capital markets, and financial operations. Work emphasizes cash forecasting, banking relationships, product development, risk and compliance considerations, and operational reporting that supports corporate treasury activities.&lt;/p&gt;
