&lt;p&gt;Interns will be involved in and support various activities which include: planning, complex modeling (financial and cash-flow), process automation, bank and treasury reporting, and&amp;nbsp; building materials for our senior leadership as well as working individually or in a group setting on a case study project that you will present to your team and the wider org.&amp;nbsp; The work will also involve collaboration with cross functional stakeholders, such as strategy and operations, sales, engineering, accounting and other teams across the finance organization.&lt;/p&gt;
