&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage your financial background to build financial and cash-flow analysis to drive insights and recommendations to business partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and use AI tools, google sheets. SQL to assist with analysis, improve process efficiencies and automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and track metrics and leading indicators of business and liquidity performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in analysis and presentation of strategic materials and treasury reporting for key management meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ship a case study project&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
