&lt;li&gt;Graduation date of December 2026 through June 2027&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and organizational skills, both written and verbal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational, problem-solving, and analytical skills&lt;/li&gt;
