&lt;li&gt;A proven ability to be a self starter capable of driving results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solution-oriented mindset with enthusiasm for establishing best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to handle multiple projects and meet deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to build strong collaborative working relationships with business partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of GSuite tools, Salesforce and MS-Office products and experience working with/analyzing contracts and large data sets using SQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will also likely have (not required):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Anaplan, SQL, Python or a willingness to learn&lt;/li&gt;
