&lt;li&gt;Process oriented mindset with desire to solve individual challenges while building for scale in mind&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and presentation skills, with the ability to speak to different functional and technical leadership both internally and externally&lt;/li&gt;
