&lt;li&gt;Ability to define and implement new business models (e.g., transforming a professional services relationship into a recurring revenue model through a platform partnership).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
